room_title: Escape room "Serial Killer" by Will You Escape? in Tucson
room_description:
In recent months, numerous Local FBI agents have attempted to locate Agent Q. Although the FBI is jubilant on their success of finding their agent’s location, dozens of other agents have been mysteriously disappearing on a daily basis. With recent threats and the surfacing of the new age serial killer donned “The Rumpelstiltskin”, many questions continue to surround the ever-growing number of missing agents.
He now has you and 3 of your friends! In 45 minutes, he will return to commit his next gruesome crime. That is unless you can escape him!
Players will be blindfolded and possibly handcuffed.
